%section
  %h4 Variable Interpolation
  %p
    Use
    %code {{variable}}
    to insert a value, or
    %code {{node_prefix.variable}}
    for a specific node's output.
  %table.ms-expr-guide-tbl
    %tr
      %td
        %code {{analyzer.score}}
      %td Score variable from the "Analyzer" node
    %tr
      %td
        %code {{user_name}}
      %td Global variable
  %p.ms-expr-guide-note
    Use the exact node prefix shown by variable discovery. Prefixes are normalized,
    and duplicate labels receive numeric suffixes.
    %br
    "Score Analyzer", "Score Analyzer" →
    %code score_analyzer
    and
    %code score_analyzer_2
